						               													<description>Action Instant excitement. Easy-to-play pocket size. Lightning-quick, action in a fast-paced dice game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Action Dice Basketball is a head-to-head dice game that can be played individually, or two players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This dice strategy game has passing, shooting, 3 pointers and drives to the hoop for dunks! Watch out for penalties and shooting fouls. 4 quarters of non stop action. It's fast, easy to learn and you call the shots. Perfect for tailgating at games, at the home or in your office, or while traveling on airplanes -- play it anywhere! Call your play, roll the dice and instantly see the results!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Dice Basketball is a head-to-head dice game that can be played individually, or two players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game can be single or two players. To play the game simply choose one of the shots roll the dice to see the result.  There are fouls, penalties, free throws, final minute shots and more.  Play conservative with 2 point calls or more risky with 3 point shots, add the score as you go and see who wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Keeping track of time in this basketball game is easy. Provided are score sheets. There are 4 quarters of basketball action. After each play is rolled, check off the circle on the score sheet while you add the score and when all the boxes are checked then the quarter is over.  If the score is tied after the 4th quarter then overtime will begin.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
